description: Keep wrapper config generic and pack-aware
globs: config/**
alwaysApply: false
---

# Config Rules

- Treat `config/` in this repo as wrapper baseline config, not pack-owned agent definitions.
- Keep `config/openclaw.json` focused on secure wrapper defaults (gateway auth, baseline models/tools, safe runtime defaults).
- Do not reintroduce pack-managed agent templates under `config/workspaces/**` in this repo.
- Prefer adding/modifying agent topology, personas, and pack-specific runtime config in `../messyvirgo-openclaw-agents`.
- Prefer wrapper-level config changes over modifying the OpenClaw source fork for deployment behavior.
